#include <iostream>
#include <vector>
#include <stdio.h>
#include <algorithm>

using namespace std;

int main() {
	
	int t, n, i;
	
	scanf("%d", &t );
	
	while( t-- ) {
		
		scanf("%d", &n );
		vector<int> A( n );
		
		for( i = 0;i < n;i++ )
			scanf("%d", &A[ i ] );

		sort( A.begin(), A.end() );
		
		for( i = 0;i < n;i++ )
			cout << A[ i ] << " ";
		cout << endl;

	}
	return 0;
}
